01:25:03,640 --> 01:25:06,200
I was brought to prison...

760
01:25:08,240 --> 01:25:09,840
tortured...

761
01:25:17,480 --> 01:25:20,200
and I recanted.

762
01:25:24,680 --> 01:25:26,720
What happened then?

763
01:25:27,520 --> 01:25:30,600
The man was burnt at stake...

764
01:25:31,200 --> 01:25:33,760
and I'm still alive.

765
01:25:56,760 --> 01:25:58,680
Brother Salvatore...

766
01:26:01,520 --> 01:26:05,360
this torment causes me
as much pain as you.

767
01:26:09,640 --> 01:26:12,400
You can end it before
we even begin.

768
01:26:12,440 --> 01:26:16,680
Open the gates ofyour heart,
search the depths ofyour soul.

769
01:26:16,800 --> 01:26:21,640
-Search!
-I'm searching, sir.

770
01:26:25,680 --> 01:26:27,680
Then tell me...

771
01:26:28,800 --> 01:26:34,680
who, among your brethren, is the
heretic responsible for these murders?

772
01:26:35,240 --> 01:26:37,760
I don't know.

773
01:26:38,000 --> 01:26:41,560
I don't know!
I know nothing!

774
01:26:46,600 --> 01:26:49,800
Stupid. I don't know anything.

775
01:26:58,680 --> 01:27:01,880
Did I lie awake that night,
suffering for the girl...

776
01:27:01,920 --> 01:27:05,480
or for myself?
I did not know.

777
01:27:05,960 --> 01:27:08,720
With the dawn, came
the emissaries of the Pope...

778
01:27:08,840 --> 01:27:12,280
our adversaries of the debate.

779
01:27:12,560 --> 01:27:17,400
But it meant so little
to me now.

780
01:27:38,720 --> 01:27:42,240
Your Eminence,
venerable brothers...

781
01:27:42,320 --> 01:27:45,960
at last we meet
for this long waiting debate!

782
01:27:46,320 --> 01:27:49,080
We've all traveled
great distances...

783
01:27:49,360 --> 01:27:51,960
to put an end to the dispute...

784
01:27:52,600 --> 01:27:58,440
that has shaken the unity...
of our Holly Mother Church.

785
01:27:59,000 --> 01:28:01,960
Good people throughout Christendom...

786
01:28:02,320 --> 01:28:05,320
are directing their gazes
at these venerable walls...

787
01:28:05,680 --> 01:28:09,600
anxiously awaiting our answer
to that question...

788
01:28:10,600 --> 01:28:15,400
"Did Christ or did he not owe...

789
01:28:15,520 --> 01:28:18,400
the clothes that He wore?"

790
01:28:28,400 --> 01:28:31,840
Beloved brethren of
the Franciscan Order...

791
01:28:31,920 --> 01:28:36,040
our Holly Father, the Pope,
has authorized me...

792
01:28:36,360 --> 01:28:41,040
and these servants
to speak on his behalf.

793
01:28:41,280 --> 01:28:45,280
The question's not whether
Christ was poor...

794
01:28:45,480 --> 01:28:49,800
But whether the Church
should be poor!

795
01:28:50,600 --> 01:28:53,080
You, Franciscans, wish to see...

796
01:28:53,320 --> 01:28:55,680
the clergy renounce
its possessions...

797
01:28:55,880 --> 01:28:57,680
and surrenderits richness.

798
01:28:57,840 --> 01:29:01,320
The abbots dissipated
their sacred treasures...

799
01:29:01,400 --> 01:29:04,400
and handed their fertile
land to the servs.

800
01:29:04,480 --> 01:29:06,000
I found the book.

801
01:29:06,440 --> 01:29:09,960
I found the book at the dispensary.
A book in Greek.

802
01:29:10,080 --> 01:29:11,920
It's behind one of my jars.

803
01:29:11,960 --> 01:29:13,440
Don't touch it.

804
01:29:13,600 --> 01:29:17,520
Return, lock your self inside.
I'll be there as soon as I can.

805
01:29:18,760 --> 01:29:24,160
...defying the Church on the resources
needed to combat the eager...

806
01:29:24,560 --> 01:29:28,080
great flow of the infident.

807
01:29:28,160 --> 01:29:32,400
You forget that even the
greatest monument to OurLord...

808
01:29:32,520 --> 01:29:38,480
is a pale reflex of
His infinite Majesty and glory.

809
01:31:15,200 --> 01:31:18,760
Brother, quick! Salvatore
confessed his heretic past...

810
01:31:18,840 --> 01:31:23,560
and yours. You have little to
escape from the flames.

811
01:31:29,480 --> 01:31:31,880
Thank you, brother.

812
01:32:03,000 --> 01:32:07,960
I consider this an absurd!
I can'tstand it!

813
01:32:08,120 --> 01:32:11,200
How dare you call the
Pope's brothel God's palace on Earth?

814
01:32:11,520 --> 01:32:13,880
-Answer that, your Eminence!
-These murders are a sign.

815
01:32:13,960 --> 01:32:18,600
-I don't believe it!
-Why not?

816
01:32:19,120 --> 01:32:21,920
Gospel speaks categorically...

817
01:32:22,000 --> 01:32:23,280
that Christ possessed
a purse!

818
01:32:23,520 --> 01:32:24,880
It's a lie, and you know it!

819
01:32:24,920 --> 01:32:28,920
Why did Our Lord tell
his disciples on seven occasions...

820
01:32:28,960 --> 01:32:32,680
not to carry neither gold
nor silver?

821
01:32:38,200 --> 01:32:41,920
You, please!

822
01:32:42,520 --> 01:32:45,200
A matter's occurred of
utmost gravity.

823
01:32:45,400 --> 01:32:48,560
Let me go! I swear
I didn't kill him!

824
01:32:48,600 --> 01:32:51,160
I was in the barn
making the inventory.

825
01:32:51,160 --> 01:32:53,560
I neverkilled anybody,
I swear it!

826
01:32:53,640 --> 01:32:56,680
Then explain us
why you were escaping.

827
01:32:58,200 --> 01:32:59,640
I wasn't.

828
01:32:59,760 --> 01:33:02,560
I've already ordered your arrest
in another choice.

829
01:33:02,720 --> 01:33:05,920
I see now that I was correct.

830
01:33:06,120 --> 01:33:09,880
If someone hadn't chosen to look
in the wrong direction...

831
01:33:09,960 --> 01:33:14,880
many men of God would
still be with us.

832
01:33:22,840 --> 01:33:27,000
"Hand above the idol,
1 and 7 of four..."

833
01:33:29,120 --> 01:33:34,680
"Use vulgar persons.
Take pleasure from the defects."

834
01:33:36,120 --> 01:33:38,840
Please, dear boy,
I'm trying to think.

835
01:33:38,920 --> 01:33:41,280
So am l, master.

836
01:33:42,560 --> 01:33:45,120
Then use your head
instead ofyour heart.

837
01:33:45,160 --> 01:33:47,080
And we can make some progress.

838
01:33:47,160 --> 01:33:50,160
Are the books more important
than people to you?

839
01:33:50,200 --> 01:33:52,000
Did I say they were?

840
01:33:52,160 --> 01:33:55,280
You never seem to care
about anyone!

841
01:33:55,640 --> 01:33:59,040
Can't you show a little pity?

842
01:34:02,680 --> 01:34:06,600
Perhaps that's the style
of my pity.

843
01:34:07,640 --> 01:34:10,720
But pity won't save her from
the fire.

844
01:34:19,160 --> 01:34:24,840
I remind all present that,
they're bound by their vow of obedience...

845
01:34:25,000 --> 01:34:27,160
and on pain of excommunication...

846
01:34:27,320 --> 01:34:32,040
to aim the lnquisitor in his
struggle against heresy.

847
01:34:32,240 --> 01:34:35,160
To sit with me
on this tribunal...

848
01:34:35,520 --> 01:34:37,920
and to share the burden
of the verdict...

849
01:34:38,080 --> 01:34:41,840
I'd require the counsel...

850
01:34:41,880 --> 01:34:44,640
of two fellowjudges.

851
01:34:55,120 --> 01:34:56,760
My lord Abbot...

852
01:34:57,840 --> 01:34:58,960
and...

853
01:35:04,560 --> 01:35:07,000
Brother William of Baskerville.

854
01:35:43,400 --> 01:35:45,400
Salvatore...

855
01:35:47,360 --> 01:35:49,360
Salvatore!

856
01:35:56,360 --> 01:36:00,120
Would you repeat your confession
of last night...

857
01:36:00,320 --> 01:36:03,640
that you and your accomplice,
Remigio de Varagine...

858
01:36:03,760 --> 01:36:06,760
were members of the heretical
Dolcinites?

859
01:36:29,280 --> 01:36:30,720
Enough!

860
01:36:33,880 --> 01:36:39,960
Remigio de Varagine, do you deny
the confession ofyour accomplice?

861
01:36:41,960 --> 01:36:45,640
No.
I don't deny it.

862
01:36:47,600 --> 01:36:50,120
I'm proud of it!

863
01:36:52,000 --> 01:36:58,280
For the twelve years I lived here...
I stuffed my belly...

864
01:36:58,720 --> 01:37:00,120
shagged my weak...

865
01:37:00,240 --> 01:37:04,400
and squeezed the hungry peasants
for dimes.

866
01:37:04,720 --> 01:37:08,320
But now you've given me strength...

867
01:37:08,440 --> 01:37:13,160
to remember what I once believed
in with all my heart.

868
01:37:13,360 --> 01:37:15,360
And for that I thank you.

869
01:37:15,440 --> 01:37:19,640
To remember that you once looted
and burnt the property of the Church?

870
01:37:19,800 --> 01:37:25,280
Yes! To give it back to
the people you stole it from!

871
01:37:25,480 --> 01:37:28,840
And did you not kill many
bishops and priests?

872
01:37:29,040 --> 01:37:33,720
Yes! I'd burn your people...

873
01:37:33,720 --> 01:37:36,720
if I had the chance!

874
01:37:43,000 --> 01:37:48,960
Holly Mary, Mother of God,
Hear my humble prayer.

875
01:37:51,080 --> 01:37:54,120
I know that my sin was
very great...

876
01:37:55,480 --> 01:38:00,840
but I beg you to not let her
suffer for my wrongdoing.

877
01:38:01,000 --> 01:38:03,120
Blessed Mother...

878
01:38:03,320 --> 01:38:07,880
many years ago you granted
a miracle by saving my master.

879
01:38:08,760 --> 01:38:12,480
Would you not do the same
for this girl?.

880
01:38:13,840 --> 01:38:18,920
My master says that the
simple folk always pay for all.

881
01:38:19,960 --> 01:38:26,240
But, please, Holly Mother,
do not let it be so.

882
01:38:27,000 --> 01:38:29,400
Guilty is that witch...

883
01:38:30,880 --> 01:38:33,840
who's seduced a monk...

884
01:38:34,000 --> 01:38:38,880
and practiced his diabolical
rituals in this holly place.

885
01:38:40,680 --> 01:38:43,080
Guilty is Salvatore...

886
01:38:44,120 --> 01:38:46,160
who's confessed his
heretical past...

887
01:38:46,320 --> 01:38:49,640
and was caught in flagrant
delito with a witch!

888
01:38:49,800 --> 01:38:53,760
Guilty is Remigio de Varagine...

889
01:38:54,160 --> 01:38:57,880
who's not regretted
his former heresies and was caught...

890
01:38:57,960 --> 01:39:00,720
trying to escape after
murdering the herbalist Severinus.

891
01:39:00,800 --> 01:39:03,880
That's a lie! I never killed
the herbalist...

892
01:39:04,000 --> 01:39:05,760
or anyone else in this abbey!

893
01:39:05,880 --> 01:39:08,240
I therefore, request you...

894
01:39:08,360 --> 01:39:11,760
to confirm my
sentence, My lord abbot.

895
01:39:16,400 --> 01:39:20,360
My heart is
full of sorrow...

896
01:39:21,080 --> 01:39:24,120
but I can't find no
reason to contest...

897
01:39:24,200 --> 01:39:27,400
the just sentence of
the Holly lnquisition.

898
01:39:29,440 --> 01:39:32,360
And you, William of Baskerville?

899
01:39:39,160 --> 01:39:42,760
Yes, he is guilty.

900
01:39:43,120 --> 01:39:45,920
Guilty of having, in his youth...

901
01:39:46,080 --> 01:39:49,280
misinterpreted the message
of the Gospels...

902
01:39:50,280 --> 01:39:54,320
and he's guilty of having
confused...

903
01:39:54,440 --> 01:39:57,840
the love of poverty with
the blind destruction...

904
01:39:57,960 --> 01:40:00,920
of wealthy and property.

905
01:40:02,080 --> 01:40:04,080
But, my lord abbot...

906
01:40:04,280 --> 01:40:09,920
he's innocent of the crimes
that've bathed your abbey in blood.

907
01:40:11,080 --> 01:40:14,800
For brother Remigio
cannot read Greek...

908
01:40:15,000 --> 01:40:18,160
and this entire mystery
hinges on...

909
01:40:18,280 --> 01:40:21,000
the theft and possession of a
book written in Greek...

910
01:40:21,080 --> 01:40:24,160
and hidden in some secret
part of the library.

911
01:40:24,880 --> 01:40:28,120
As the verdict of the
lnquisition was disputed by William...

912
01:40:28,280 --> 01:40:31,800
we must extract the
prisoner's confession.

913
01:40:31,960 --> 01:40:34,760
Take him to the forge
and show him the instruments.

914
01:40:36,080 --> 01:40:41,320
I'll confess anything you
want, but don't torture me.

915
01:40:41,400 --> 01:40:44,120
I can't go through a night
like Salvatore!

916
01:40:44,280 --> 01:40:48,360
Very well.
Why did you kill them?

917
01:40:49,160 --> 01:40:54,520
Why? I don't know why.

918
01:40:56,000 --> 01:41:00,360
-Because you were inspired by the devil?
-Yes... that's it.

919
01:41:00,440 --> 01:41:07,160
I was inspired by the devil.
I'm inspired by the devil!

920
01:41:08,160 --> 01:41:11,360
Adralmech, Lucifer,
I call for you...

921
01:41:11,440 --> 01:41:13,000
Lords of Hell.

922
01:41:18,840 --> 01:41:21,560
The shepherd has done
his duty...

923
01:41:21,640 --> 01:41:26,120
and the infected sheep must
now be consigned to the purifying flames!

924
01:41:26,280 --> 01:41:28,600
You may burn brother Remigio...

925
01:41:29,000 --> 01:41:33,120
but you won't put a stop for the
crimes being committed in this abbey!

926
01:41:33,280 --> 01:41:35,600
Other monks will meet
death here...

927
01:41:35,640 --> 01:41:40,280
and they'll also have
black fingers and black tongues!

928
01:41:41,560 --> 01:41:43,040
Your Eminence, I beg you...

929
01:41:43,160 --> 01:41:46,160
we, Franciscans, are disappointed
with brother William.

930
01:41:46,200 --> 01:41:49,680
Once more we've seen that
your theories protect heretics...

931
01:41:49,920 --> 01:41:53,080
and lead to murder.
The debate's concluded.

932
01:41:53,160 --> 01:41:56,920
Brother William
has relaxed...

933
01:41:58,040 --> 01:42:01,280
into the errors of which
he was formerly perjured.

934
01:42:01,440 --> 01:42:05,320
Having sought yet again
to shield a heretic...

935
01:42:05,440 --> 01:42:08,440
from just punishment by
the lnquisition...

936
01:42:08,520 --> 01:42:11,520
He'll come with me
to Avignon for confirmation...

937
01:42:11,600 --> 01:42:13,480
of my sentence by Pope John.

938
01:42:28,920 --> 01:42:30,640
I'm right.

939
01:42:32,400 --> 01:42:37,200
Ifonlyl could find the book
andprove that Gui was wrong!

940
01:42:37,400 --> 01:42:41,240
But the Antichrist
was victorious once more...

941
01:42:41,440 --> 01:42:46,200
and nothing seemed to be
able to hinder him.

942
01:42:52,000 --> 01:42:53,400
Come on.

943
01:43:22,680 --> 01:43:25,560
When the pyres are light
tonight...

944
01:43:25,640 --> 01:43:28,120
Let the flames purify...

945
01:43:28,200 --> 01:43:31,280
each of us
in his own heart.

946
01:43:31,480 --> 01:43:35,360
Let's return to what was,
and ever should be...

947
01:43:35,440 --> 01:43:37,520
the office of this abbey:

948
01:43:37,560 --> 01:43:40,080
the preservation of
knowledge.

949
01:43:40,200 --> 01:43:45,520
Preservation, I said.
Not search for...

950
01:43:45,640 --> 01:43:50,360
because there's no progress
in the history of knowledge...

951
01:43:50,440 --> 01:43:55,360
merely a continuous
and sublime recapitulation.

952
01:43:56,080 --> 01:43:58,720
Let's now pray oh mighty...

953
01:43:59,000 --> 01:44:03,280
that the blood-eyed antichrist...

954
01:44:03,400 --> 01:44:07,400
has been removed from our
sacred precincts...

955
01:44:07,480 --> 01:44:12,320
and our monastery
has returned to peace.

956
01:44:19,720 --> 01:44:24,520
The fifth trumpet had
the power of a thousand scorpions...

957
01:44:24,600 --> 01:44:27,000
-He told me.
-Who told you?

958
01:44:27,120 --> 01:44:30,000
His tongue's black
and his finger's black...

959
01:44:30,040 --> 01:44:32,440
as brother William foretold!

960
01:44:46,320 --> 01:44:47,920
It's brother Malachia, father.

961
01:44:48,080 --> 01:44:49,480
-Malachia?
-Yes, father.

962
01:44:49,560 --> 01:44:53,040
Dear God! Not Malachia!

963
01:44:53,520 --> 01:44:56,040
Will it never end?

964
01:45:06,160 --> 01:45:08,600
William of Baskerville
was right. He said...

965
01:45:08,720 --> 01:45:11,920
Yes! He knew!

966
01:45:12,040 --> 01:45:15,440
Just as I'd have known,
if I'd been the murderer!

967
01:45:15,560 --> 01:45:17,680
Find William
of Baskerville!

968
01:45:17,920 --> 01:45:19,400
We can't open the mirror!

969
01:45:19,480 --> 01:45:23,000
Perhaps pressing the 1a and the
7a letters of the word "four".

970
01:45:23,160 --> 01:45:24,520
But "four" only has 4 letters.

971
01:45:24,600 --> 01:45:28,640
In Latin, "quatuor". Remember
the inscription of the mirror?

972
01:45:28,720 --> 01:45:30,400
We had to press above
the idol.

973
01:45:30,520 --> 01:45:34,160
Not "idolum" as in Latin,
but "eidolon" as in Greek.

974
01:45:34,360 --> 01:45:39,320
Meaning "image: or
"reflection". Our own reflection!

975
01:45:41,320 --> 01:45:44,600
-This way, master!
-No, this way, Adso.

976
01:46:31,760 --> 01:46:34,240
Here... Q and R.

977
01:46:35,400 --> 01:46:38,200
Pray God we're
not mistaken.

978
01:46:48,560 --> 01:46:50,240
Come.

979
01:47:14,680 --> 01:47:17,280
Good evening, Venerable Jorge.

980
01:47:24,040 --> 01:47:28,560
I've been expecting you
these several days past, William.

981
01:47:28,640 --> 01:47:32,240
You must've flown
to this chamber to reach it ahead of us.

982
01:47:32,400 --> 01:47:34,680
You've discovered many things...

983
01:47:34,880 --> 01:47:37,360
since your arrival at
this abbey...

984
01:47:37,480 --> 01:47:42,440
but the shortcut through
the labyrinth isn't among them.

985
01:47:42,720 --> 01:47:46,360
So now, what's it that you want?

986
01:47:47,880 --> 01:47:52,360
I want to see the book
in Greek you said was never written.

987
01:47:52,520 --> 01:47:56,640
A book entirely devoted to comedy,
which you hate...

988
01:47:56,720 --> 01:47:59,640
as much as you hate laughter.

989
01:48:01,200 --> 01:48:05,640
I want to see what's probably
the only the surviving copy...

990
01:48:07,120 --> 01:48:09,520
of the 2nd book of the
poetics ofAristotle.

991
01:48:09,600 --> 01:48:15,600
William, what a magnificent
librarian you'd have been!

992
01:48:15,640 --> 01:48:20,800
Here's your well done
reward.

993
01:48:21,880 --> 01:48:26,520
Read it. Leaf its secrets.

994
01:48:29,640 --> 01:48:31,680
You've won.

995
01:48:40,520 --> 01:48:41,640
